Day 4: Keep It Simple!
🔍 "Complexity kills progress. Simplicity sparks action."  
👉 Tip: Keep processes and solutions simple. Simplifying work fosters clarity and boosts team productivity.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
